The scope for the project will be to select and deploy a modern Data Integration solution in support of the overall Enterprise Performance Management program that includes the major functions of the global organization, including:
* Commercial 
* Supply Chain 
* Research & Development
* Labor & Headcount 
* Global / Corporate Functions
* Consolidations / External Reporting

And, across the following regions of Johnson & Johnson’s operations, including:
* North America (NA)
* Latin America (LA)
* Europe, Middle East and Africa (EMEA)
* Asia Pacific (APAC)

And, across all sectors of Johnson & Johnson’s operations, including:
* Consumer
* Medical Devices
* Pharmaceuticals
* Vision Care
* Corporate
